,000 Gravity Coins on purchase!\n\nTo be the best, you have to beat the best.\n\nOnline League coming soon!", "short_description": "Welcome to Gravity League - a brand new ball game!\n\nThe rules are simple - 2 players, 1 ball, no gravity - the first player to get 7 points is the winner!\n\nCompete with the best of the best and make your way to the top of the league to become a Gravity legend!\n\n*** Early bird specials - \n- Launch discounted price!\n- Get 5,000 Gravity Coins on purchase!\n\nTo be the best, you have to beat the best.\n\nOnline League coming soon!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://blue-duck-studios.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Blue Duck Studios Ltd.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://blue-duck-studios.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1592192974313489"}, {"id": "2776542286000603"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "901413484182591"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 4, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "548733791078442"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1021210842709675"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "759656188883420"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "5776768012407397"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "548733791078442"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1729897140, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "548733791078442"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supp